Cars and taxis, symbols of urban mobility, traverse the road, while pedestrians add a human element to the scene. The color palette is dominated by shades of gray and brown, reflecting the urban landscape, with occasional splashes of green from the trees lining the street providing a touch of nature amidst the concrete jungle.
